## PROJECT STRUCTURE

```
src/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ modules/              # Feature modules (route-based grouping)
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ [feature]/
‚îÇ       ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ components/   # Feature-specific components
‚îÇ       ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ hooks/        # Feature-specific hooks
‚îÇ       ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ api/          # React Query queries & mutations (hand-written or Orval-generated)
‚îÇ       ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ store/        # Zustand slices (if needed)
‚îÇ       ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ types.ts      # Feature types
‚îÇ       ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ index.ts      # Public exports
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ components/           # Shared/common UI components
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ ui/               # shadcn/ui generated components (do not edit manually)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ hooks/                # Shared custom hooks
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ lib/                  # Utilities, helpers, constants
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ generated/            # Orval-generated API hooks & types (do not edit manually)
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ router/               # React Router route definitions
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ index.tsx
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ types/                # Global TypeScript types
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ App.tsx
```

- Group by **feature/route**, not by file type (no flat `/components`, `/hooks`, `/services` at root)
- Common components used across features live in `src/components/`
- Co-locate tests next to the file they test: `Component.test.tsx`

