## NAMING

| Item | Convention | Example |
|---|---|---|
| Components | PascalCase | `UserProfileCard` |
| Hooks | camelCase, `use` prefix | `useUserProfile` |
| Context | PascalCase + `Context` suffix | `AuthContext` |
| Event handlers | `handle` prefix | `handleSubmit`, `handleDelete` |
| Boolean state | `is` / `has` / `can` prefix | `isLoading`, `hasError` |
| Query keys | Descriptive arrays | `['users', userId]` |

